from gryphon the golden gryphon subject re intel the pentium and linux inabu arnd burghardt write hi folk yesterday i visit the cebit hannover germany where intel wa present the pentium processor they have fmy in word machine with thi beast run so they present it nicely unly by run picture show thi i could do on a the presentor promise it to be binary compatible to the and i say i do believe i show him a linux-system emergency disk with patch lilo to boot from disk and say him convice me boot thi no gut no glory a he decide no glory he wo let anybody touch hi holy cow and not even boot a suspect o i think by myself be the coward of the day and go back to earth what cn we learn thi technology be far from industrial-standart so you can expect thi beast in ymy local computer-shop at least in spring next year only my ye only ymy here mine if i be run at a new chip at a trade show and have little to no real technical knowledge i would let some stranger with a diskette boot my demo machine if the demo machine be down too long person will not see my nice demo and if thi purposted linux diskette be really something that will wipe the disk or be load with a viru i in deep trouble no marketer in their right mind would let you do thi unles they have specifically invite person to do so and provide machine to do it with we can we learn thi technology will be ship from pc vendor in may and will be compatible the golden gryphon gryphon the crown jewel of the american prison system president bill clinton on live in the white house openage the premier sco unix integrator in the washington area 